69
70static char *i2s_ASN1_IA5STRING(X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method, ASN1_IA5STRING *ia5);
71static ASN1_IA5STRING *s2i_ASN1_IA5STRING(X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method, X509V3_CTX *ctx, char *str);
72const X509V3_EXT_METHOD v3_ns_ia5_list[] = {
73EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_base_url),
74EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_revocation_url),
75EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_ca_revocation_url),
76EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_renewal_url),
77EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_ca_policy_url),
78EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_ssl_server_name),
79EXT_IA5STRING(NID_netscape_comment),
80EXT_END
81};
82
83
84static char *i2s_ASN1_IA5STRING(X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method,
85 ASN1_IA5STRING *ia5)
86{
87 char *tmp;
88 if(!ia5 || !ia5->length) return NULL;
89 if(!(tmp = OPENSSL_malloc(ia5->length + 1))) {
90 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE);
91 return NULL;
92 }
93 memcpy(tmp, ia5->data, ia5->length);
94 tmp[ia5->length] = 0;
95 return tmp;
96}
97
98static ASN1_IA5STRING *s2i_ASN1_IA5STRING(X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method,
99 X509V3_CTX *ctx, char *str)
100{
101 ASN1_IA5STRING *ia5;
102 if(!str) {
103 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, X509V3_R_INVALID_NULL_ARGUMENT);
104 return NULL;
105 }
106 if(!(ia5 = M_ASN1_IA5STRING_new())) goto err;
107 if(!ASN1_STRING_set((ASN1_STRING *)ia5, (unsigned char*)str,
108 strlen(str))) {
109 M_ASN1_IA5STRING_free(ia5);
110 goto err;
111 }
112 return ia5;
113 err:
114 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(X509V3, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE);
115 return NULL;
116}
